1396
01:50:19,376 --> 01:50:21,310
Sit back, you fucking freak!

1397
01:50:21,378 --> 01:50:22,936
Shut your fucking mouth!

1398
01:50:24,447 --> 01:50:28,884
You're no messiah. You're a movie
of the week. A fucking tee-shirt...

1399
01:50:29,285 --> 01:50:30,809
at best.

