1403
01:50:58,748 --> 01:51:01,512
The Lord works in mysterious ways.

1404
01:51:03,753 --> 01:51:06,187
Do you see those high tension towers?

1405
01:51:06,256 --> 01:51:08,087
That's where we're headed.

1406
01:51:08,158 --> 01:51:10,752
I see it. 9 o'clock,
and follow that road.

